title: Becoming a Whole-Hearted Wife, Part 2
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: Your upbringing may be manifesting in your marriage in ways you don't even notice. John and Greg talk about recognizing the signs and avoiding unhealthy patterns. Featuring Erin Smalley.
